<Base
  title="Services — Meish Experience Ops"
  description="Experience Ops for hospitality and aviation: on-site Experience Audits, the Clara guest-signal system, and the Flight Experience Audit."
>
  <section class="section container">
    <p class="eyebrow">Services</p>
    <h1>The customer buys the outcome. Meish owns the process.</h1>
    <p class="lead">Meish runs two complementary lanes for hospitality — with a parallel line
      for aviation.</p>

    <h2>Pre-arrival — before the guest arrives</h2>
    <p><a href="/services/clara"><strong>Clara by Meish</strong></a> — the Guest Signal System.
      Clara helps the hotel hear the guest before the guest arrives, and turns guest questions
      into hotel intelligence.</p>

    <h2>On-site — during the stay</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/services/experience-audits"><strong>Meish Experience Audit</strong></a> —
        human-state observation, friction mapping, and an actionable improvement plan. From €3,500.</li>
      <li><a href="/services/cleanliness-audits"><strong>Cleanliness Experience Audit</strong></a> —
        cleanliness as felt trust, not just a technical checklist.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>In the air</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/services/aviation"><strong>Flight Experience Audit</strong></a> —
        the audit method, adapted to the passenger journey.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>The audit ladder (hotels)</h2>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr><th>Tier</th><th>Product</th><th>Outcome</th><th>From</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Entry</td><td><strong>Meish Experience Signal Audit</strong></td><td>10 ranked friction points + 10 fixes + debrief</td><td>€3,500</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Core</td><td><strong>Meish Experience Hotel Audit</strong></td><td>Scored journey map · Meish Experience Score · 30-day plan</td><td>€7,500</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Premium</td><td><strong>Meish Experience Transformation Sprint</strong></td><td>Workshops + 30–90 day implementation support</td><td>€25,000</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <p><small>Prices exclude VAT. Bands are indicative and confirmed per property.</small></p>

    <h2>Not what you might expect</h2>
    <p>Not mystery shopping. Not staff surveillance. Not a quality manual. We measure the
      invisible architecture of human experience — read the <a href="/philosophy">philosophy</a>
      and our <a href="/privacy">boundaries</a>.</p>

    <p><a class="button button--primary" href="/contact">Start with one Signal Audit</a></p>
  </section>
